      <title>印度停止接收通过Sovcomflot油轮交付的俄罗斯石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国的制裁，所有印度炼油厂现在都拒绝接收 PJSC Sovcomflot 油轮上运载的俄罗斯原油，这使得自两年前入侵乌克兰以来蓬勃发展的贸易进一步复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</guid>
